|--| Nova |--|
|------------|

Nova is a lightweight language for conversing with computers.
It's flexible, makes no assumptions, and allows for exploration and good conversation.
Nova lets you write what you mean.

|an axe, a tree|
    a log

|the button was pressed, the door is closed|
    the door is open

|the button was pressed, the door is open|
    the door is closed

|todo list|
    wash dishes,
    sweep floors,
    get groceries,
    feed pets

|| an axe, a tree,
   the button was pressed, the door is closed,
   todo list
